{"id":"e9887d2a-55b3-4f4d-a63d-8e598f4cd27c","title":"1471/05/27: footnote 1","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"908a6685-cbda-49ec-9cb6-fc5cb70a0fd9","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Some writers place this fact in 1472, and others in 1474, some mistake the year and not the month; but Landucci states the truth, which is confirmed by the following two extracts taken from the Archives of the Opera di Santa Maria del Fiore. On the 28th May, 1471, 2 lire 8 soldi given to Marchione, servant of the Opera (Administrative Office), to buy bread and wine for the workmen when they put up the ball. And on the 1st June 3 lire paid to the trumpeters of the Palagio; taken by Matteo di Madonna Andreagia, to be given them for their trouble when they played on the lantern when the cross was put up (Quaderna di Cassa, ad an).","standoffProperties":[{"id":"e7092e7a-ac0a-44ac-b905-f25df88ea980","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":103,"end":110,"value":"5d9cbd12-a35b-4b1c-9130-36c6786145b2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"579924a6-2d60-44d6-971d-fbdf4a7bb966","type":"style/italics","start":210,"end":239,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e64fdf2f-e7b0-40fe-a59f-a4fce4883625","type":"codex/time-reference","start":249,"end":262,"value":"004599c2-92f6-435c-9767-374cb3421602","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6d358ee9-8a6e-4904-be5b-0fd54be4633e","type":"style/superscript","start":251,"end":252,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ccfdcde6-0305-40e9-b2b9-6d1566dc6c8b","type":"style/italics","start":265,"end":319,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0d7c733a-5aad-44e6-aa01-4935eeb05bbc","type":"style/italics","start":346,"end":409,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"70112191-c3eb-446f-919f-54f28e888436","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":405,"end":408,"value":"42bf1ef3-d89b-427f-9b71-1f2981c422c2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"208ba815-f6ee-431b-a9d6-c390102e1c0a","type":"codex/